   The user asked me to analyze the MediaLightbox component (`/user_c042661f/Documents/reigh/src/shared/components/MediaLightbox/MediaLightbox.tsx`) to understand why it's so large (2672 lines) and propose smart abstractions to restructure it. After I presented a holistic 5-phase plan, the user explicitly requested: "Can you please proceed with this. Run through every phase in sequential order, sense-checking each upon completion, before continuing to the next."

2. Key Technical Concepts:
   - React component architecture and composition
   - Props drilling elimination via Context
   - Dialog/overlay event handling (pointer, touch, click, z-index checking)
   - Radix UI Dialog primitives
   - Hook orchestration patterns
   - Layout routing (DesktopSidePanelLayout, MobileStackedLayout, CenteredLayout)
   - Segment slot mode for video segment editing
   - Task pane integration
   - Body scroll locking for modals
   - Double-tap detection for mobile close

